==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adapter
<hw>A*dapt"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who adapts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A connecting tube; an
adopter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- 2. any device connecting two parts of an apparatus (e.g. tubes of
different diameters, or electric cords with different plug types); a
device allowing an apparatus to be used for purposes other than
originally intended --></p>

<p><ent>Adaption</ent>⟦br⟧
